00:15:23,760 --> 00:15:26,000
 drvo Josipovo i Izrelovih plemena,

519
00:15:26,000 --> 00:15:27,060
 njegovih savjeznika,

520
00:15:27,060 --> 00:15:29,360
 i sastavit ću ga s drvetom judinim,

521
00:15:29,360 --> 00:15:31,100
 te ću od njih načiniti jedno.

522
00:15:31,100 --> 00:15:33,560
 Ova će biti jedno u moje ruci.

523
00:15:33,560 --> 00:15:35,440
 Imate motiv drva,

524
00:15:35,440 --> 00:15:36,720
 dva komada drva,

525
00:15:36,720 --> 00:15:39,320
 kako se mogu spojiti dva komada drva?

526
00:15:39,320 --> 00:15:41,180
 Kako ih može spojiti?

527
00:15:41,180 --> 00:15:43,640
 Drvo fiksom, je li tako u Ezekielo vrijeme?

528
00:15:43,640 --> 00:15:44,920
 Ok.

529
00:15:44,920 --> 00:15:47,160
 Tako da ih ukrstiš, je li tako?

530
00:15:47,160 --> 00:15:48,860
 Tako da ih ukrstiš.

531
00:15:48,860 --> 00:15:50,760
 Sveti oci, crkveni oci,

532
00:15:50,760 --> 00:15:52,180
 kad sam to otkrio onako,

533
00:15:52,180 --> 00:15:55,460
 malo ti se zacakliti sve oči,

534
00:15:55,460 --> 00:15:57,020
 ono je ovdje kaže,

535
00:15:57,020 --> 00:15:59,500
 križ je taj koji će ujediniti plamena.

536
00:15:59,500 --> 00:16:01,540
 Imate drvo,

537
00:16:01,540 --> 00:16:03,420
 u kojem ćeš upisati dva plamena,

538
00:16:03,420 --> 00:16:06,420
 to je judino drvo,

539
00:16:06,420 --> 00:16:07,700
 imat ćeš Izrelovo drvo,

540
00:16:07,700 --> 00:16:08,940
 nije ostalih deset plamena,

541
00:16:08,940 --> 00:16:10,460
 i stavi ih u jedno.

542
00:16:10,460 --> 00:16:12,620
 Križ je taj koji će ujediniti,

543
00:16:12,620 --> 00:16:13,500
 kako će išev,

544
00:16:13,500 --> 00:16:15,300
 sin čovječi išev iznak Mesija,

545
00:16:15,300 --> 00:16:17,340
 ujediniti dvadaest plamena

546
00:16:17,340 --> 00:16:18,620
 raspršenih Izrelovih,

547
00:16:18,860 --> 00:16:19,720
 preko križe.

548
00:16:19,720 --> 00:16:22,140
 Zato ta motiv drva.

549
00:16:22,140 --> 00:16:23,100
 Pitaš se, dobro,

550
00:16:23,100 --> 00:16:24,480
 kakav je to način spajanja,

551
00:16:24,480 --> 00:16:26,220
 ujedinjavanja, natrag, jel?

552
00:16:26,220 --> 00:16:27,220
 Uzmeš drvo, drvo,

553
00:16:27,220 --> 00:16:28,400
 lupiš se po glavi i kaži,

554
00:16:28,400 --> 00:16:29,820
 daj se već namo zaberite, jel?

555
00:16:29,820 --> 00:16:31,380
 Dobro, ok.

556
00:16:31,380 --> 00:16:33,080
 Evo, vrlo, vrlo jedan snažen motiv,

557
00:16:33,080 --> 00:16:33,920
 ovdje u,

558
00:16:33,920 --> 00:16:37,460
 iz Ezekijel,

559
00:16:37,460 --> 00:16:37,920
 ponavljam,

560
00:16:37,920 --> 00:16:40,800
 Ezekijel 3.7.15.24.

561
00:16:40,800 --> 00:16:42,580
 I sada pogledajte dalje,

562
00:16:42,580 --> 00:16:44,300
 što to ujedinjenje,

563
00:16:44,300 --> 00:16:45,760
 isto i dalje smo na Ezekijelu,

564
00:16:45,760 --> 00:16:47,820
 što to ujedinjenje podrazumljeva.

565
00:16:47,820 --> 00:16:51,140
 Oba drveta na koja to napišeš,

566
00:16:51,140 --> 00:16:52,160
 neka ti budu u ruci,

567
00:16:52,160 --> 00:16:53,100
 njima nauči gled,

568
00:16:53,100 --> 00:16:53,840
 i reci,

569
00:16:53,840 --> 00:16:55,340
 ovako govori gospodin,

570
00:16:55,340 --> 00:16:55,620
 evo,

571
00:16:55,620 --> 00:16:57,040
 skupit ću sinove Izrelovi,

572
00:16:57,040 --> 00:16:59,440
 Izrelovi iz naroda u koje dođoše,

573
00:16:59,440 --> 00:17:00,740
 skupit ću ih odasvud

574
00:17:00,740 --> 00:17:02,260
 i odvesti ih u zemlju njihovu.

575
00:17:02,260 --> 00:17:02,780
 Tu je problem.

576
00:17:02,780 --> 00:17:03,820
 Izrelovi sinovi,

577
00:17:03,820 --> 00:17:04,420
 ne judini,

578
00:17:04,420 --> 00:17:06,240
 nego Izrelovi sinovi,

579
00:17:06,240 --> 00:17:07,580
 njih deset koji su raspršeni

580
00:17:07,580 --> 00:17:08,480
 među drugim narodima,

581
00:17:08,480 --> 00:17:09,540
 poganskim narodima.

582
00:17:09,540 --> 00:17:11,600
 I načinit ću od njih

583
00:17:11,600 --> 00:17:12,680
 jedan narod u zemlji,

584
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:13,780
 u gorama Izrelovi,

585
00:17:13,780 --> 00:17:15,480
 i bit će im svima jedan kralj.

586
00:17:15,480 --> 00:17:17,600
 I oni više neće biti dva naroda,

587
00:17:17,600 --> 00:17:19,220
 i neće više biti razljenjeni

588
00:17:19,220 --> 00:17:20,380
 na dva kraljevstva.

589
00:17:20,380 --> 00:17:22,060
 I neće se više kaljati,

590
00:17:22,060 --> 00:17:22,780
 ovo je važno,

591
00:17:22,780 --> 00:17:24,140
 neće se više kaljati

592
00:17:24,140 --> 00:17:25,100
 svojim kumirima,

593
00:17:25,100 --> 00:17:26,440
 ni svojim grozotama,

594
00:17:26,440 --> 00:17:27,460
 ni opačimama.

595
00:17:27,520 --> 00:17:30,700
 izbavit ću ih od svih

596
00:17:30,700 --> 00:17:32,540
 njihovih nevjera

597
00:17:32,540 --> 00:17:33,580
 kojima zgrješiše

598
00:17:33,580 --> 00:17:34,760
 i očistit ću ih

599
00:17:34,760 --> 00:17:36,040
 i oni će biti moj narod,

600
00:17:36,040 --> 00:17:37,660
 a ja njihov Bog.

601
00:17:37,660 --> 00:17:38,780
 I sluga moj David

602
00:17:38,780 --> 00:17:39,740
 bit će im kralj

603
00:17:39,740 --> 00:17:41,460
 i svima će im biti

604
00:17:41,460 --> 00:17:42,300
 jedan pastir.

605
00:17:42,300 --> 00:17:45,820
 Kada imate Davida

606
00:17:45,820 --> 00:17:48,760
 u spisima proročkim,

607
00:17:48,760 --> 00:17:51,080
 David je uvijek slika Mesije.

608
00:17:51,080 --> 00:17:52,380
 On je mesijanski lik,

609
00:17:52,380 --> 00:17:53,460
 sjetite se i sami.

610
00:17:53,460 --> 00:17:55,360
 Kao što David,

611
00:17:56,140 --> 00:17:58,940
 kao što je David,

612
00:17:58,940 --> 00:17:59,800
 ajmo reći,

613
00:17:59,800 --> 00:18:00,740
 slika,

614
00:18:00,740 --> 00:18:01,700
 prototip,

615
00:18:01,700 --> 00:18:03,240
 onoga što će Mesija

616
00:18:03,240 --> 00:18:03,620
 jednoga,

617
00:18:03,620 --> 00:18:04,540
 znači Krist

618
00:18:04,540 --> 00:18:05,740
 jednoga dana učiniti.

619
00:18:05,740 --> 00:18:06,920
 Dakle,

620
00:18:06,920 --> 00:18:08,080
 tako i ono izlazak,

621
00:18:08,080 --> 00:18:08,660
 sjetite se,

622
00:18:08,660 --> 00:18:09,260
 paska što smo

623
00:18:09,260 --> 00:18:10,180
 zadnji puta radili,

624
00:18:10,180 --> 00:18:12,180
 stara paska je zapravo

625
00:18:12,180 --> 00:18:13,800
 predznak onoga što će

626
00:18:13,800 --> 00:18:15,040
 Isus učiti na Euharisti.

627
00:18:15,040 --> 00:18:17,940
 A ako nešto je staro

628
00:18:17,940 --> 00:18:19,180
 i samo je predznak,

629
00:18:19,180 --> 00:18:20,840
 ono ne može biti bolje

630
00:18:20,840 --> 00:18:23,440
 od onoga što će doći

631
00:18:23,440 --> 00:18:24,060
 na kraju.

632
00:18:24,060 --> 00:18:25,260
 Znači, nova paska

633
00:18:25,260 --> 00:18:26,540
 mora biti tišću puta

634
00:18:26,540 --> 00:18:27,620
 bolje od stare paske

635
00:18:27,620 --> 00:18:28,900
 i novi mesija

636
00:18:28,900 --> 00:18:30,060
 mora biti tišću puta

637
00:18:30,060 --> 00:18:31,120
 sarušeniji i bolji

638
00:18:31,120 --> 00:18:32,340
 od staroga mesije,

639
00:18:32,340 --> 00:18:32,800
 Davida.

640
00:18:32,800 --> 00:18:34,200
 Kaj, u kraju sad ne treba

641
00:18:34,200 --> 00:18:34,700
 da pravi to što

642
00:18:34,700 --> 00:18:35,520
 napravim s bat čepom

643
00:18:35,520 --> 00:18:36,460
 i to je to već i bolje,

644
00:18:36,460 --> 00:18:36,900
 ali tako?

645
00:18:36,900 --> 00:18:38,960
 Razumijete,

646
00:18:38,960 --> 00:18:39,860
 svaki puta

647
00:18:39,860 --> 00:18:41,220
 kada imate Davida,

648
00:18:41,220 --> 00:18:43,400
 riječ je o mesijanskom liku.

649
00:18:43,400 --> 00:18:44,200
 Tako i ovdje.

650
00:18:44,580 --> 00:18:45,420
 i sluga moj David

651
00:18:45,420 --> 00:18:46,180
 bit će im kralj,

652
00:18:46,180 --> 00:18:47,640
 naravno se misle na mesiju,

653
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:48,660
 i svima će im biti

654
00:18:48,660 --> 00:18:49,240
 jedan pastor.

655
00:18:49,240 --> 00:18:50,200
 Ali ovaj dio,

656
00:18:50,200 --> 00:18:50,960
 isto ovaj motiv,

657
00:18:50,960 --> 00:18:52,340
 dakle imate motiv križa,

658
00:18:52,340 --> 00:18:52,920
 kao što sam rekao,

659
00:18:52,920 --> 00:18:53,460
 ova dva drva,

660
00:18:53,460 --> 00:18:55,540
 i od čega će ih izbaviti,

661
00:18:55,540 --> 00:18:56,480
 od njihovih nevjera,

662
00:18:56,480 --> 00:18:58,040
 kojima zgrješiše,

663
00:18:58,040 --> 00:18:58,500
 kumira,

664
00:18:58,500 --> 00:18:59,020
 grozota,

665
00:18:59,020 --> 00:18:59,600
 opačina

666
00:18:59,600 --> 00:19:00,520
 i očistit će ih.

667
00:19:00,520 --> 00:19:02,860
 To je ono što podrazumijeva

668
00:19:02,860 --> 00:19:04,180
 spajanje,

669
00:19:04,180 --> 00:19:05,520
 dakle opet skupljanje.

670
00:19:05,520 --> 00:19:07,780
 Evo vidite taj motiv spasenja

671
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:08,580
 od grijeha,

672
00:19:08,580 --> 00:19:09,360
 isto ovdje.

673
00:19:09,360 --> 00:19:11,100
 Rabin Jonan,

674
00:19:11,100 --> 00:19:11,800
 idemo malo sada

675
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:13,620
 u židovsku tradiciju,

676
00:19:13,620 --> 00:19:15,380
 Rabin Johanan,

677
00:19:15,380 --> 00:19:15,700
 pardon,

678
00:19:15,700 --> 00:19:16,220
 ne Jonan,

679
00:19:16,220 --> 00:19:16,760
 Johanan,

680
00:19:16,760 --> 00:19:18,900
 u Babiloskom Talnudu,

681
00:19:18,900 --> 00:19:20,700
 Pesahim 88a,

682
00:19:20,700 --> 00:19:21,260
 kaže,

683
00:19:21,260 --> 00:19:23,280
 koliko je važno židovsko pitanje

684
00:19:23,280 --> 00:19:25,840
 opet sabiranja tih,

685
00:19:25,840 --> 00:19:26,120
 dakle,

686
00:19:26,120 --> 00:19:26,520
 plemena,

687
00:19:26,520 --> 00:19:26,840
 kaže,

688
00:19:27,240 --> 00:19:28,620
 u Babiloskom Talmudu,

689
00:19:28,620 --> 00:19:30,620
 polovno sabiranje izgnadnika

690
00:19:30,620 --> 00:19:33,060
 važno je koliko je sam dan

691
00:19:33,060 --> 00:19:34,800
 kada su stvarani nebo i zemlja.

692
00:19:34,800 --> 00:19:36,640
 Jer to je nešto,

693
00:19:36,640 --> 00:19:37,140
 dakle,

694
00:19:37,140 --> 00:19:39,220
 taj dan će biti bažan,

695
00:19:39,220 --> 00:19:41,320
 čak i bažniji od onog početka,

696
00:19:41,320 --> 00:19:41,540
 dakle,

697
00:19:41,540 --> 00:19:42,440
 ovo će biti na kraju,

698
00:19:42,440 --> 00:19:43,820
 kao neka je skatologija.

699
00:19:43,820 --> 00:19:44,440
 Dakle,

700
00:19:44,440 --> 00:19:45,780
 to sabiranje plemena,

701
00:19:45,780 --> 00:19:46,360
 dakle,

702
00:19:46,360 --> 00:19:47,300
 to je važno,

703
00:19:47,300 --> 00:19:48,680
 gotovo kao i onaj dan,

704
00:19:48,680 --> 00:19:49,600
 ako ne i važnije,

705
00:19:49,600 --> 00:19:51,840
 kada su stvarani nebo i zemlja.

706
00:19:51,840 --> 00:19:53,460
 Sam početak svih početaka,

707
00:19:53,460 --> 00:19:53,660
 jel?

708
00:19:54,520 --> 00:19:55,900
 E, sada idemo do našega Isusa.

709
00:19:55,900 --> 00:19:57,820
 Gdje je on tu u cijeloj priči?

710
00:19:57,820 --> 00:19:59,320
 Kako se on tu snašao

711
00:19:59,320 --> 00:20:00,620
 ili nije snašao?

712
00:20:00,620 --> 00:20:01,440
 Naravno da se snašao,

713
00:20:01,440 --> 00:20:02,280
 ali ljubo vidjeti kako.

714
00:20:02,280 --> 00:20:04,060
 Dakle,

715
00:20:04,060 --> 00:20:06,560
 Isus je polovno sabiranje prognanih.

716
00:20:08,240 --> 00:20:08,620
 ovako,

717
00:20:08,620 --> 00:20:10,520
 Mate 19, 28,

718
00:20:10,520 --> 00:20:12,240
 tu već vidimo ovako malo naznake,

719
00:20:12,240 --> 00:20:13,000
 ali vidjet ćemo

720
00:20:13,000 --> 00:20:15,240
 koji je bio konkretan znak,

721
00:20:15,240 --> 00:20:16,480
 jedno konkretno čudo,

722
00:20:16,480 --> 00:20:18,340
 kojim on,

723
00:20:18,340 --> 00:20:19,500
 dakle,

724
00:20:19,500 --> 00:20:20,480
 objašnjava,

725
00:20:20,480 --> 00:20:21,460
 da je on taj

726
00:20:21,460 --> 00:20:23,260
 koji će preko gozbe

727
00:20:23,260 --> 00:20:25,180
 sabrati 12

728
00:20:25,180 --> 00:20:26,980
 izgubljenih izredovih plamena.

729
00:20:26,980 --> 00:20:27,760
 Međutim,

730
00:20:27,760 --> 00:20:28,480
 idemo prvo vidjeti.

731
00:20:28,480 --> 00:20:30,220
 Mate 19, 28 kaže ovo.

732
00:20:30,220 --> 00:20:31,580
 Reče je Isus.

733
00:20:32,240 --> 00:20:33,400
 Zaista kaže vam,

734
00:20:33,400 --> 00:20:35,120
 vi koji pođu ste za mnom

735
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:35,740
 o preporodu,

736
00:20:35,740 --> 00:20:36,040
 dakle,

737
00:20:36,040 --> 00:20:36,820
 prvo kontekst,

738
00:20:36,820 --> 00:20:37,660
 ovdje Petar,

739
00:20:37,660 --> 00:20:38,640
 u ovom dijelu,

740
00:20:38,640 --> 00:20:39,680
 Petar pita,

741
00:20:39,680 --> 00:20:41,100
 Isus ovdje odgovara Petru,

742
00:20:41,100 --> 00:20:41,980
 a njegovo pitanje,

743
00:20:41,980 --> 00:20:42,900
 mi koji smo sve ostavili,

744
00:20:42,900 --> 00:20:43,700
 pošli za tobom,

745
00:20:43,700 --> 00:20:44,500
 što ćemo dobiti?

746
00:20:44,500 --> 00:20:44,720
 Znamo,

747
00:20:44,720 --> 00:20:45,680
 Petar je uvijek pragmatičan,

748
00:20:45,680 --> 00:20:46,580
 ajde, reci.

749
00:20:46,580 --> 00:20:48,960
 Sad bez veze idemo za tobom,

750
00:20:48,960 --> 00:20:49,660
 ali na kraju ništa.

751
00:20:49,660 --> 00:20:51,920
 I sada reče im Isus.

752
00:20:51,920 --> 00:20:52,820
 Zaista kaže,

753
00:20:52,820 --> 00:20:54,160
 vi koji pođu ste za mnom

754
00:20:54,160 --> 00:20:54,900
 o preporodu,

755
00:20:54,900 --> 00:20:56,420
 kad sin čovječi sjede

756
00:20:56,420 --> 00:20:57,720
 na prijestolje svoje slave

757
00:20:57,720 --> 00:20:59,080
 i vi ćete sjediti

758
00:20:59,080 --> 00:21:00,740
 na 12 prijestolja

759
00:21:00,740 --> 00:21:03,000
 i suditi 12 plemena Izrelovih.

760
00:21:03,000 --> 00:21:03,980
 Ovako,

761
00:21:03,980 --> 00:21:06,040
 uvijek je problem

762
00:21:06,040 --> 00:21:07,980
 objašnjavati nama,

763
00:21:07,980 --> 00:21:08,860
 katolicima,

764
00:21:08,860 --> 00:21:09,620
 neke stvari

765
00:21:09,620 --> 00:21:11,680
 i kad nešto citiramo,

766
00:21:11,680 --> 00:21:12,140
 jer onako,

767
00:21:12,140 --> 00:21:13,040
 uzimamo zdravo za gotovo.

768
00:21:13,040 --> 00:21:14,080
 To smo čuli toliko puta,

769
00:21:14,080 --> 00:21:14,920
 ali opet kažem,

770
00:21:14,920 --> 00:21:15,900
 stavite se malo

771
00:21:15,900 --> 00:21:17,280
 u poziciju onih

772
00:21:17,280 --> 00:21:18,580
 koji tada prvi puta

773
00:21:18,580 --> 00:21:19,920
 slušaju ove Isusove riječi

774
00:21:19,920 --> 00:21:21,000
 i ovo što Isus čini.

775
00:21:21,000 --> 00:21:22,880
 Prvo što Isus čini,

776
00:21:22,880 --> 00:21:24,140
 dakle,

777
00:21:24,140 --> 00:21:25,240
 u noći molitve,

778
00:21:25,420 --> 00:21:27,960
 njegov prije svoga javnoga nastupa,

779
00:21:27,960 --> 00:21:29,440
 što zove

780
00:21:29,440 --> 00:21:31,260
 i izabire 12 oricu.

781
00:21:31,260 --> 00:21:33,740
 Kao svaki drugi pravi,

782
00:21:33,740 --> 00:21:34,880
 pobožni židov

