 Dakle,

1051
00:27:12,800 --> 00:27:14,740
 svi narodi sabraćaju se sva plemena,

1052
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:16,180
 zastor koji pokrivaš,

1053
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:18,060
 sve narode će se maknuti i tako dalje.

1054
00:27:18,060 --> 00:27:18,660
 Dakle,

1055
00:27:18,660 --> 00:27:20,540
 ovdje Isus govori,

1056
00:27:20,540 --> 00:27:23,520
 zašto govori i o skupljanju

1057
00:27:23,520 --> 00:27:25,580
 poganskih naroda?

1058
00:27:25,580 --> 00:27:26,680
 Zašto?

1059
00:27:26,680 --> 00:27:28,700
 Zato što su židovi,

1060
00:27:28,700 --> 00:27:29,500
 kažem,

1061
00:27:29,500 --> 00:27:30,760
 govorimo o Sjevernom kraljevstvu,

1062
00:27:30,760 --> 00:27:32,200
 zato sam to pocrtao na početku,

1063
00:27:32,200 --> 00:27:33,640
 u Sjevernom kraljevstvu

1064
00:27:33,640 --> 00:27:34,940
 su se već pomješali,

1065
00:27:34,940 --> 00:27:36,060
 smješali s poganima.

1066
00:27:36,060 --> 00:27:38,000
 Neki se već i smatraju poganima,

1067
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:39,020
 ne više židovima.

1068
00:27:39,020 --> 00:27:40,980
 I zato je važno to,

1069
00:27:40,980 --> 00:27:42,640
 neko od vas možda pod NK

1070
00:27:42,640 --> 00:27:44,020
 jeste isto židova da ne zna.

1071
00:27:44,020 --> 00:27:45,300
 Na primjer,

1072
00:27:45,300 --> 00:27:46,040
 pa da, pa što?

1073
00:27:46,040 --> 00:27:47,900
 Moramo to provjeriti.

1074
00:27:47,900 --> 00:27:49,760
 E sada,

1075
00:27:49,760 --> 00:27:50,900
 što mislite,

1076
00:27:50,900 --> 00:27:52,060
 koje Isus

1077
00:27:52,060 --> 00:27:53,420
 znamenje čini,

1078
00:27:53,420 --> 00:27:56,160
 u kojem želi predstaviti sebe

1079
00:27:56,160 --> 00:27:58,000
 i pokazuje se kao onaj

1080
00:27:58,000 --> 00:27:58,980
 koji

1081
00:27:58,980 --> 00:28:01,280
 ispunjava ovo što je Izaija rekao

1082
00:28:01,280 --> 00:28:02,340
 o mesijanskoj gozbi.

1083
00:28:02,340 --> 00:28:03,880
 Ovo što sam malo prije pročitao.

1084
00:28:03,880 --> 00:28:05,420
 Što mislite,

1085
00:28:05,420 --> 00:28:05,980
 koje čuda,

1086
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:06,700
 koje znamenje?

1087
00:28:06,700 --> 00:28:08,720
 Jedno od najvažnijih,

1088
00:28:08,720 --> 00:28:10,060
 najsnažnijih čuda koje čini.

1089
00:28:10,060 --> 00:28:11,040
 Nije baš bilo kapo.

1090
00:28:12,300 --> 00:28:12,820
 Ok.

1091
00:28:12,820 --> 00:28:15,280
 Kad Isus dva put hrani mnoštvo.

1092
00:28:15,280 --> 00:28:16,960
 Vrlo jednostavno.

1093
00:28:16,960 --> 00:28:17,900
 Dva put hrani mnoštvo.

1094
00:28:17,900 --> 00:28:19,540
 Slažite da dva put hrani mnoštvo?

1095
00:28:19,540 --> 00:28:20,220
 Ne samo jedan put,

1096
00:28:20,220 --> 00:28:20,880
 nego dva put.

1097
00:28:20,880 --> 00:28:22,420
 Pogledajte sad ovo.

1098
00:28:22,420 --> 00:28:24,620
 Dakle, prvi puta,

1099
00:28:24,620 --> 00:28:25,520
 ako se sjećate,

1100
00:28:25,520 --> 00:28:28,140
 prvi puta hrani mnoštvo,

1101
00:28:28,140 --> 00:28:30,020
 Matej 14 i Marko 6

1102
00:28:30,020 --> 00:28:30,700
 o tome govore,

1103
00:28:30,700 --> 00:28:31,760
 kad imamo pet kruhova

1104
00:28:31,760 --> 00:28:32,440
 i dvije ribice,

1105
00:28:32,440 --> 00:28:34,380
 a drugi puta hrani mnoštvo,

1106
00:28:34,380 --> 00:28:36,420
 Matej 15 i Marko 8,

1107
00:28:36,420 --> 00:28:37,840
 kad ima sedam kruhova

1108
00:28:37,840 --> 00:28:38,800
 i nekoliko ribica.

1109
00:28:38,800 --> 00:28:40,580
 E sada imamo malo u simboliku.

1110
00:28:40,580 --> 00:28:41,760
 Idemo se malo poigrati

1111
00:28:41,760 --> 00:28:42,680
 i nemo vidjeti

1112
00:28:42,680 --> 00:28:44,520
 što to zapravo konkretno znači

1113
00:28:44,520 --> 00:28:45,500
 i koja je povezanost

1114
00:28:45,500 --> 00:28:46,980
 s ome što je Izaija rekao.

1115
00:28:46,980 --> 00:28:48,720
 Na kraju kraja Isus se to pita.

1116
00:28:48,720 --> 00:28:51,200
 Isus, kada očini ta čuda,

1117
00:28:51,200 --> 00:28:52,600
 pita svoje učenike,

1118
00:28:52,600 --> 00:28:54,160
 jeste skužili što sam sad napravio?

1119
00:28:54,160 --> 00:28:56,900
 Kaže Marko 8, 14 do 22.

1120
00:28:58,020 --> 00:29:00,560
 A apostoli zaboraviše podjeti kruha.

1121
00:29:00,560 --> 00:29:02,860
 Oni uvijek nemaju kruha,

1122
00:29:02,860 --> 00:29:04,760
 traže žice druge da jedu,

1123
00:29:04,760 --> 00:29:06,220
 nikak da ulove ribe,

1124
00:29:06,220 --> 00:29:07,720
 pravi katolici.

1125
00:29:07,720 --> 00:29:08,760
 Ok.

1126
00:29:08,760 --> 00:29:11,600
 Nostop gladi tamo tržu nešto i tako.

1127
00:29:11,600 --> 00:29:12,760
 Onda Isu ima s njima problema,

1128
00:29:12,760 --> 00:29:14,680
 onda ih nostop pred farizejeva

1129
00:29:14,680 --> 00:29:15,560
 mora opravdavati

1130
00:29:15,560 --> 00:29:17,920
 i vuču neke aseve iz rukava.

1131
00:29:17,920 --> 00:29:19,240
 Ok, dobro.

1132
00:29:19,240 --> 00:29:20,560
 E sad.

1133
00:29:20,560 --> 00:29:22,300
 A zaboraviše podjeti kruha.

1134
00:29:22,300 --> 00:29:23,720
 Imali su samo jedan kruh

1135
00:29:23,720 --> 00:29:24,760
 sa sobom na lađi.

1136
00:29:24,760 --> 00:29:26,440
 Dato ih Isus opomenu.

1137
00:29:26,820 --> 00:29:29,080
 Pazite, čujete se kvasa farizejskog

1138
00:29:29,080 --> 00:29:30,180
 i kvasa Herodova.

1139
00:29:30,180 --> 00:29:32,500
 Oni zamišljali među sobom govorahu.

1140
00:29:32,500 --> 00:29:33,440
 Kruha nemamo.

1141
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,860
 Ono, pusti sad to o farizejima,

1142
00:29:34,860 --> 00:29:35,440
 gladni smo.

1143
00:29:35,440 --> 00:29:37,240
 Mislite, ponekad mi malo smiješilo.

1144
00:29:37,240 --> 00:29:38,200
 Dijelo je, ali dobro.

1145
00:29:38,200 --> 00:29:39,100
 Ok.

1146
00:29:39,860 --> 00:29:41,480
 Zamijetio to Isus, pa im reče.

1147
00:29:41,480 --> 00:29:44,280
 Zašto ste zamišljali što kruha nemate?

1148
00:29:44,280 --> 00:29:46,660
 Zar još ne skvačate i ne razumijete?

1149
00:29:46,660 --> 00:29:48,180
 Zar vam je srce stvrnuto?

1150
00:29:48,180 --> 00:29:49,700
 Oči imate, a ne vidite.

1151
00:29:49,700 --> 00:29:50,940
 Uši imate, a ne čujete.

1152
00:29:50,940 --> 00:29:52,360
 Zar se ne sjećate?

1153
00:29:52,360 --> 00:29:55,940
 Kad sam ono razlomio pet kruhova na pet tisuća,

1154
00:29:55,940 --> 00:29:58,000
 koliko punih košera ulomaka odnijeste?

1155
00:29:58,000 --> 00:29:59,180
 Kažu mu dvanest.

1156
00:29:59,180 --> 00:30:02,080
 A kad razlovi ih sedam na četiri tisuće,

1157
00:30:02,080 --> 00:30:04,240
 koliko punih košera ulomaka odnijeste?

1158
00:30:04,240 --> 00:30:05,300
 Odgovore sedam.

1159
00:30:05,300 --> 00:30:07,620
 A učenjima još ne razumijete.

1160
00:30:07,620 --> 00:30:09,600
 Jer razumijete?

1161
00:30:09,600 --> 00:30:11,340
 Još ne razumijete?

1162
00:30:11,340 --> 00:30:13,800
 Ne razumijem ja.

1163
00:30:13,800 --> 00:30:14,640
 Zaključujemo.

1164
00:30:14,640 --> 00:30:15,580
 Idemo doma.

1165
00:30:15,580 --> 00:30:16,400
 Ok.

1166
00:30:16,400 --> 00:30:19,720
 Dakle, Isus ovdje sam,

1167
00:30:19,720 --> 00:30:22,000
 upravo u ovom dialogu,

1168
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:22,720
 želi pokazati,

1169
00:30:22,720 --> 00:30:24,860
 napravio sam jedan znak, jedno znamenje.

1170
00:30:24,860 --> 00:30:26,640
 Nešto sam želio poručiti time,

1171
00:30:26,640 --> 00:30:27,900
 tim hranjenjem noštva.

1172
00:30:28,220 --> 00:30:29,420
 i uvijeti što konkretno.

1173
00:30:29,420 --> 00:30:30,560
 Ovako.

1174
00:30:30,560 --> 00:30:32,700
 Bilo bi jednostavnije da,

1175
00:30:32,700 --> 00:30:33,740
 ovako tablicu,

1176
00:30:33,740 --> 00:30:34,840
 jer sam napravio tablicu,

1177
00:30:34,840 --> 00:30:35,800
 prvo hranjenje mnoštva

1178
00:30:35,800 --> 00:30:36,680
 i drugo hranjenje mnoštva.

1179
00:30:36,680 --> 00:30:37,620
 Napravimo paralelu.

1180
00:30:37,620 --> 00:30:39,240
 Uvijemo koja je simbolika.

1181
00:30:39,240 --> 00:30:39,640
 Ali dobro.

1182
00:30:39,640 --> 00:30:43,140
 Dobro, ok.

1183
00:30:43,140 --> 00:30:44,960
 Znači, prvo hranjenje mnoštva.

1184
00:30:44,960 --> 00:30:47,260
 Imamo pet kruhova i dvije ribice.

1185
00:30:47,260 --> 00:30:48,760
 U drugom hranjenju mnoštva

1186
00:30:48,760 --> 00:30:50,920
 imamo sedam kruhova i nekoliko ribica.

1187
00:30:50,920 --> 00:30:52,380
 U prvom hranjenju

1188
00:30:52,380 --> 00:30:55,260
 nahranjeno je pet tisuća ljudi.

1189
00:30:55,260 --> 00:30:57,560
 U drugom hranjenju sa sedam kruhova

1190
00:30:57,560 --> 00:30:59,180
 nahranjeno je četiri tisuće.

1191
00:30:59,180 --> 00:31:00,280
 Pratite.

1192
00:31:00,280 --> 00:31:01,040
 Ok.

1193
00:31:01,040 --> 00:31:02,020
 Gledajmo dalje.

1194
00:31:02,020 --> 00:31:04,140
 Prvo hranjenje mnoštva

1195
00:31:04,140 --> 00:31:05,360
 se događa gdje?

1196
00:31:05,360 --> 00:31:06,400
 Sad imamo vidjeti mjesto.

1197
00:31:06,400 --> 00:31:07,960
 Vrlo važno, vrlo znakovito.

1198
00:31:07,960 --> 00:31:09,580
 Na židovskom teritoriju.

1199
00:31:09,580 --> 00:31:10,960
 Dakle, i vidim to

1200
00:31:10,960 --> 00:31:12,900
 Marko 6.42 govori,

1201
00:31:12,900 --> 00:31:14,460
 ali Galilea 6.42.

1202
00:31:14,460 --> 00:31:15,500
 I to vidimo,

1203
00:31:15,500 --> 00:31:15,940
 zanimljivo,

1204
00:31:15,940 --> 00:31:17,400
 i jezično se ovdje poigrava,

1205
00:31:17,400 --> 00:31:18,020
 da znamo da smo

1206
00:31:18,020 --> 00:31:19,380
 na židovskom teritoriju

1207
00:31:19,380 --> 00:31:20,540
 kod prvog hranjenja mnoštva.

1208
00:31:20,940 --> 00:31:21,980
 Kad on za košare,

1209
00:31:21,980 --> 00:31:23,360
 dakle, koliko je ostalo?

1210
00:31:23,360 --> 00:31:24,360
 12 košara.

1211
00:31:24,360 --> 00:31:25,980
 Kad on za košare koristi

1212
00:31:25,980 --> 00:31:27,900
 u grčkom tekstu

1213
00:31:27,900 --> 00:31:28,820
 hebriski izraz.

1214
00:31:28,820 --> 00:31:29,700
 Kofinos.

1215
00:31:29,700 --> 00:31:31,980
 Kofinos nije grčki izraz za košare,

1216
00:31:31,980 --> 00:31:32,780
 nego hebriski.

1217
00:31:32,780 --> 00:31:33,760
 Dakle, želi

1218
00:31:33,760 --> 00:31:35,660
 12 kofinosa je ostalo.

1219
00:31:35,660 --> 00:31:36,920
 I to je vrlo jednostavno.

1220
00:31:36,920 --> 00:31:38,600
 12 prvo u prvom

1221
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:39,760
 i koga nahranio,

1222
00:31:39,760 --> 00:31:42,300
 12 plamena Izraela.

1223
00:31:42,300 --> 00:31:43,860
 Dakle, simbolika 12 košara,

1224
00:31:43,860 --> 00:31:45,240
 12 plamena Izraela.

1225
00:31:45,240 --> 00:31:46,600
 12 košara je preostalo.

1226
00:31:46,600 --> 00:31:47,920
 Imo sad na drugo.

1227
00:31:47,920 --> 00:31:50,280
 Drugo hranjenje mnošta,

1228
00:31:50,280 --> 00:31:51,740
 rekao smo na hranjenoj 4.000,

1229
00:31:51,740 --> 00:31:53,460
 i ono se događa gdje?

1230
00:31:53,460 --> 00:31:55,080
 Na poganskom teritoriju.

1231
00:31:55,080 --> 00:31:56,180
 Tir i Sidon.

1232
00:31:56,180 --> 00:31:57,580
 I košare,

1233
00:31:57,580 --> 00:31:59,200
 Marko 8.8,

1234
00:31:59,200 --> 00:32:00,940
 nemaju hebriski izraz

1235
00:32:00,940 --> 00:32:02,160
 kao u prvog hranjenju,

1236
00:32:02,160 --> 00:32:03,260
 nego baš konkretan

1237
00:32:03,260 --> 00:32:04,160
 grčki izraz,

1238
00:32:04,160 --> 00:32:05,320
 a to je Spurida.

1239
00:32:05,320 --> 00:32:06,440
 Dakle, košare.

1240
00:32:06,440 --> 00:32:07,540
 Sedam košara.

1241
00:32:07,540 --> 00:32:09,660
 12 je vrlo jednostavno,

1242
00:32:09,660 --> 00:32:10,920
 12 plamena Izraela ovih,

1243
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:12,020
 nahranio je židove.

1244
00:32:12,020 --> 00:32:14,480
 Dakle, govori o mesijanskoj gozbi

1245
00:32:14,480 --> 00:32:16,420
 sa židovskim izabralim narodom.

1246
00:32:16,420 --> 00:32:18,260
 A ovdje, zašto sedam?

1247
00:32:18,260 --> 00:32:19,660
 Ovdje nije sad stvar simbolika

1248
00:32:19,660 --> 00:32:22,080
 biblijskog broja sedam savršenstva,

1249
00:32:22,080 --> 00:32:22,880
 nego što?

1250
00:32:22,880 --> 00:32:25,800
 Što označilo sedam preostalih košara?

1251
00:32:25,800 --> 00:32:27,600
 Dakle, to su poganski

1252
00:32:27,600 --> 00:32:29,480
 da sedam je broj naroda

1253
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:31,680
 koje je izabrali narod našao

1254
00:32:31,680 --> 00:32:33,040
 kad je ušao u kanan.

1255
00:32:33,260 --> 00:32:36,420
 I to ono što će dijela apostolska reči 13.19.

1256
00:32:36,420 --> 00:32:38,600
 Pa pošto zatre sedam naroda

1257
00:32:38,600 --> 00:32:39,660
 u zemlji kananskoj,

1258
00:32:39,660 --> 00:32:42,880
 ubašljeni ga u zemlji njihovoj.

1259
00:32:42,880 --> 00:32:45,420
 Polođeni zakonik 7.1 to i kaže.

1260
00:32:45,980 --> 00:32:49,940
 Kad te gospodin Bog tvoj uvede u zemlju koju ideš da je zaposjedeš

1261
00:32:49,940 --> 00:32:52,220
 i kad ispred tebe otjera mnoge narode

1262
00:32:52,220 --> 00:32:57,580
 hetite, gjergašane, amorejce, kanance, perižane, hivice

1263
00:32:57,580 --> 00:32:59,180
 i naše najdraže jebusejce,

1264
00:32:59,180 --> 00:33:02,060
 sedam naroda brojnih i jačih od tebe.

1265
00:33:02,060 --> 00:33:03,820
 Sedam naroda brojnih i jačih od tebe.

1266
00:33:04,700 --> 00:33:05,540
 Evo, to je mesijansko.

1267
00:33:05,540 --> 00:33:08,360
 Isus je ovim dva put hrani mnoštvo

1268
00:33:08,360 --> 00:33:10,600
 i ima, dakle, sad ovo,

1269
00:33:10,600 --> 00:33:12,560
 a učinjima još ne razumijete.

1270
00:33:12,560 --> 00:33:13,380
 Sad razumijete?

1271
00:33:13,380 --> 00:33:15,620
 Ok, razumijete, dobro.

1272
00:33:15,620 --> 00:33:16,760
 Dakle, to je to.

1273
00:33:16,760 --> 00:33:20,940
 Pretilina gozba zastiraše sve narode.

1274
00:33:20,940 --> 00:33:23,440
 Riječ je, prvo ide židovima,

1275
00:33:23,440 --> 00:33:25,400
 a onda ide i poganima.

1276
00:33:25,760 --> 00:33:29,060
 I to u toj mesijanskoj gozbi želi, dakle,

1277
00:33:29,060 --> 00:33:30,860
 povezati jedne i druge.

1278
00:33:30,860 --> 00:33:33,600
 Zato, sada vidimo da mesijanska gozba

1279
00:33:33,600 --> 00:33:35,220
 ima univerzalni značaj.

1280
00:33:35,220 --> 00:33:37,680
 Ne samo za židove, nego i za pogane.

1281
00:33:37,680 --> 00:33:40,100
 Zato je to sada jasno.

1282
00:33:40,100 --> 00:33:44,860
 I zato u Matej 8.11.12 kaže ovo.

1283
00:33:44,860 --> 00:33:48,480
 A kaže vam, mnogi će s istoka i zapada

1284
00:33:48,480 --> 00:33:51,120
 doći i sjesti za sol s Abrahamom,

1285
00:33:51,120 --> 00:33:53,280
 Izakom, Jakom u kraljivstvu nebeskom.

1286
00:33:53,280 --> 00:33:55,700
 A sinovi će kraljivstva biti izbačeni

1287
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:56,540
 van u tabu.

1288
00:33:56,540 --> 00:33:59,200
 Ovdje će biti blač i škrgut zubi.

1289
00:33:59,200 --> 00:34:00,540
 Pogledajte sad ovo.

1290
00:34:00,540 --> 00:34:03,100
 On govori ovdje o poganima.

1291
00:34:03,100 --> 00:34:04,440
 Zašto? Jer on ne kaže,

1292
00:34:04,440 --> 00:34:06,620
 mnogi će sa sjevera i juga,

1293
00:34:06,620 --> 00:34:09,580
 jer to su židovi, sjeverno i južno kraljivstvo,

1294
00:34:09,580 --> 00:34:11,440
 nego s istoka i zapada,

1295
00:34:11,440 --> 00:34:14,240
 istok i zapad je riječ o poganskim narodima,

1296
00:34:14,240 --> 00:34:16,460
 doći i sad, ovo je šokantno.

1297
00:34:16,460 --> 00:34:17,960
 Isus ovdje šokira.

1298
00:34:17,960 --> 00:34:19,820
 Židove, zašto?

1299
00:34:19,820 --> 00:34:21,440
 Ovo nama najnormalnija rečenica.

1300
00:34:21,440 --> 00:34:23,700
 Ali što je ovo šokantno?

1301
00:34:24,280 --> 00:34:25,420
 Da će pogani,

1302
00:34:25,420 --> 00:34:27,920
 nečisti, nevjernici,

1303
00:34:27,920 --> 00:34:29,980
 sjesti za stol

1304
00:34:29,980 --> 00:34:31,700
 sa židovskim patrijarcima,

1305
00:34:31,700 --> 00:34:33,620
 Abrahamom, Izakom i Jakvom.

1306
00:34:33,620 --> 00:34:35,380
 Jel židovi jedu sa nežidovima?

1307
00:34:35,380 --> 00:34:36,000
 Ne.

1308
00:34:36,000 --> 00:34:37,240
 Mislim, ne.

1309
00:34:37,240 --> 00:34:38,800
 U Isusov vrijeme, ne.

1310
00:34:38,800 --> 00:34:40,060
 Da se ne one čiste.

1311
00:34:40,060 --> 00:34:41,640
 Dakle, ovdje Isus šokira.

1312
00:34:41,640 --> 00:34:42,680
 Kako će pogani?

1313
00:34:42,680 --> 00:34:44,000
 I to ne sa bilo kojim židovima.

1314
00:34:44,000 --> 00:34:46,320
 Nego sa pravocima naše vjere.

1315
00:34:46,320 --> 00:34:47,120
 Jel?

1316
00:34:47,120 --> 00:34:49,280
 Dakle, i zato je ovdje riječ

1317
00:34:49,280 --> 00:34:51,760
 kraljivstvo, nebesko-mesijanska,

1318
00:34:51,760 --> 00:34:53,060
 nadnaravna gozba.

1319
00:34:53,060 --> 00:34:54,820
 Nadnaravna gozba.

1320
00:34:54,820 --> 00:34:57,040
 Po čemu znamo da mesijanska gozba

1321
00:34:57,040 --> 00:34:58,520
 nije ovozemaljska gozba,

1322
00:34:58,520 --> 00:35:00,840
 ovo što sam pročitao kod proroka Izaije,

1323
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:01,860
 nego nadnaravna,

1324
00:35:01,860 --> 00:35:03,000
 zašto ta gozba,

1325
00:35:03,000 --> 00:35:03,760
 dakle,

1326
00:35:03,760 --> 00:35:05,460
 će maknuti zastručno,

1327
00:35:05,460 --> 00:35:06,600
 zastiraše sve narode,

1328
00:35:06,600 --> 00:35:08,540
 to ne može obično naklopiti u McDonald'su.

1329
00:35:08,540 --> 00:35:09,440
 Dakle,

1330
00:35:09,440 --> 00:35:12,140
 uništiće smrt za svakda tom gozbom.

1331
00:35:12,140 --> 00:35:12,580
 Jel?

1332
00:35:12,580 --> 00:35:14,640
 Dakle, recite mi koji obrok

1333
00:35:14,640 --> 00:35:16,100
 zemaljski to može učiniti.

1334
00:35:16,100 --> 00:35:17,960
 Dakle, i kod proroka Izaije,

1335
00:35:17,960 --> 00:35:20,800
 mesijanska gozba jednako nadnaravna gozba.

1336
00:35:20,800 --> 00:35:23,120
 Evo, čisto da znate.

1337
00:35:23,120 --> 00:35:23,360
 Evo.

1338
00:35:23,360 --> 00:35:25,400
 Dobro, i sada pogledajte,

1339
00:35:25,400 --> 00:35:28,160
 nebeska gozba u židovskoj tradiciji.

1340
00:35:28,160 --> 00:35:29,400
 Opet ću malo konzultirati

1341
00:35:29,400 --> 00:35:31,800
 židovske spise i židovske predaje.

1342
00:35:32,100 --> 00:35:33,520
 Ne samo Bibliju.

1343
00:35:33,520 --> 00:35:34,720
 Dakle,

1344
00:35:34,720 --> 00:35:36,100
 spise zove

1345
00:35:36,100 --> 00:35:38,700
 Egzodus Rabah 25.8.

1346
00:35:38,700 --> 00:35:39,560
 Kaže ovo.

1347
00:35:39,560 --> 00:35:42,100
 Drugo objašnjenje,

1348
00:35:42,100 --> 00:35:43,180
 vrlo lako, lijepo.

1349
00:35:43,180 --> 00:35:44,900
 Drugo objašnjenje riječi,

1350
00:35:44,900 --> 00:35:46,980
 on će prebivati u visinama.

1351
00:35:46,980 --> 00:35:48,300
 Dakle, kontekst,

1352
00:35:48,300 --> 00:35:50,860
 ovdje se želi objasniti

1353
00:35:50,860 --> 00:35:52,680
 iz proroka Izaije 33.16.

1354
00:35:52,680 --> 00:35:53,920
 Rečenica,

1355
00:35:53,920 --> 00:35:55,300
 on će prebivati u visinama.

1356
00:35:55,300 --> 00:35:56,840
 Vidjet ćemo, dakle,

1357
00:35:56,840 --> 00:35:58,000
 da je ovdje židovi,

1358
00:35:58,000 --> 00:36:00,760
 neovisno sad samo i o svetome pismu,

1359
00:36:00,820 --> 00:36:01,940
 nego i u svojoj tradiciji,

1360
00:36:01,940 --> 00:36:03,460
 su svjesni toga

1361
00:36:03,460 --> 00:36:04,580
 da nije riječ

1362
00:36:04,580 --> 00:36:06,140
 o političkoj gozbi,

1363
00:36:06,140 --> 00:36:07,160
 diplomatskoj,

1364
00:36:07,160 --> 00:36:08,460
 o političkom mesiji

1365
00:36:08,460 --> 00:36:10,400
 i da je ta gozba nadnaravna,

1366
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:12,100
 da će biti u visinama,

1367
00:36:12,100 --> 00:36:13,520
 u kraljevstvu nebeskom.

1368
00:36:13,520 --> 00:36:14,320
 Dakle,

1369
00:36:14,320 --> 00:36:15,280
 drugo objašnjenje riječi,

1370
00:36:15,280 --> 00:36:16,640
 on će prebivati u visinama.

1371
00:36:16,980 --> 00:36:17,560
 Pisano je,

1372
00:36:17,560 --> 00:36:20,960
 da gospodin bog tvoj vodite u dobru zemlju,

1373
00:36:20,960 --> 00:36:22,480
 ponovljanje zakonik 8.7,

1374
00:36:22,480 --> 00:36:25,600
 da vidiš stol koji je pripremljen na nebu,

1375
00:36:25,600 --> 00:36:26,740
 kao što se kaže,

1376
00:36:26,740 --> 00:36:30,220
 ići ću pred gospodinom u zemlji živih,

1377
00:36:30,220 --> 00:36:30,520
 pardon,

1378
00:36:30,520 --> 00:36:31,700
 psalam 116.

1379
00:36:31,700 --> 00:36:32,760
 On,

1380
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:33,320
 bog,

1381
00:36:33,320 --> 00:36:36,020
 kao da će sjediti nad patrijarcima,

1382
00:36:36,020 --> 00:36:39,960
 a patrijarci i svi pravednici će sjediti u njemu samome.

1383
00:36:39,960 --> 00:36:41,500
 Vrlo mistično.

1384
00:36:41,900 --> 00:36:42,800
 Kao što se kaže,

1385
00:36:42,800 --> 00:36:44,440
 pred tvojim su ležali nogama,

1386
00:36:44,440 --> 00:36:46,200
 ponovljanje zakonik 33.3,

1387
00:36:46,200 --> 00:36:48,540
 i on će im davati hrane.

1388
00:36:48,540 --> 00:36:54,920
 Gospodin u kraljevstvu nebeskom u visinama će hraniti pravednike.

1389
00:36:54,920 --> 00:36:56,860
 Donje će, što?

1390
00:36:56,860 --> 00:37:00,280
 Donje će im plod iz Edenskog vrta.

1391
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:03,280
 Evo sad, ovdje vi katolici imate dopuštenje

1392
00:37:03,280 --> 00:37:06,020
 smatrati ono što se već kod Adama i Eve dogodilo,

1393
00:37:06,020 --> 00:37:07,300
 da je predznak Euharistije.

1394
00:37:07,300 --> 00:37:10,500
 Sami židovi svoje tradicije lijepo ovdje kažu.

1395
00:37:10,940 --> 00:37:13,200
 Donje će im plod iz Edenskog vrta

1396
00:37:13,200 --> 00:37:15,280
 i hraniće ih iz drva života.

1397
00:37:15,280 --> 00:37:17,300
 Tko će biti...

1398
00:37:17,300 --> 00:37:18,220
 Evo je sad zadimljivo.

1399
00:37:18,220 --> 00:37:19,660
 Ovo je ovako simpatišno malo.

1400
00:37:19,660 --> 00:37:21,080
 I sada pitanje je,

1401
00:37:21,080 --> 00:37:23,440
 tko će biti prvi koji će...

1402
00:37:23,440 --> 00:37:27,920
 Ajmo reći, koji će se pomoliti na početku ručka, gozbe, jel?

1403
00:37:27,920 --> 00:37:30,860
 Dakle, tko će biti prvi koji će dati blagoslov i zahvalu?

1404
00:37:30,860 --> 00:37:32,260
 Ovako.

1405
00:37:32,260 --> 00:37:37,640
 Svi će ponizno zamoliti Boga da odredi onoga koji će izreći blagoslov i zahvaliti.

1406
00:37:37,640 --> 00:37:39,460
 E sada ide ovako.

1407
00:37:39,580 --> 00:37:42,020
 On će odrediti Mihajla, Arkadžela Mihajla.

1408
00:37:42,020 --> 00:37:46,320
 Onda će Mihajl, kaže, ne, odrediti Gabriela.

1409
00:37:46,320 --> 00:37:48,880
 Gabriela će odrediti patriarhija.

1410
00:37:48,880 --> 00:37:52,720
 A oni, patriarci, će dati čast Davidu.

1411
00:37:53,460 --> 00:37:54,880
 Dakle, opet mesijanski lik.

1412
00:37:54,880 --> 00:38:01,580
 Govoreći, dosto da i priliči se da zemaljski kralj blagoslovi i pozdravi nebeskog kralja.

1413
00:38:01,580 --> 00:38:08,900
 Oni će predati čašu Davidu, koji će reći, uzet ću čašu spasenja i zazvati ime gospodine.

1414
00:38:09,720 --> 00:38:12,960
 Vrlo snažno ovaj dio iz židovske tradicije.

1415
00:38:12,960 --> 00:38:15,500
 Dakle, mesijanska gozba kao nadnaravna gozba.

1416
00:38:15,500 --> 00:38:19,620
 Vidite, ko će se tamo sjediti i kako će se ovdje prepirati, ko će se pomoliti na početku.

1417
00:38:19,620 --> 00:38:21,360
 Kao i mi, ono, kad smo kod nekog.

1418
00:38:21,540 --> 00:38:24,060
 Dakle, ko će se pomoliti, ne ti, ne ti svečanik, pa se pomoliti.

1419
00:38:24,060 --> 00:38:25,040
 Ok.

1420
00:38:25,040 --> 00:38:31,700
 Dobro, e sada, konkretno, pred sam kraj finale, a to je ovo.

1421
00:38:31,700 --> 00:38:36,300
 Posljednja večera, ja vam ovo sa mesijanskom gozbom jasno, je li tako?

1422
00:38:36,300 --> 00:38:40,640
 Dakle, koja je važna, dakle, preko mesijanske gozbe, to je ključ.

1423
00:38:40,640 --> 00:38:48,520
 To je oruđe, alat, metoda, kojom gospodin, vidimo preko proroka i u samoživskoj tradiciji je to opisano,

1424
00:38:48,520 --> 00:38:51,420
 će sabrati raspršena Izrailova plemena.

1425
00:38:52,060 --> 00:38:58,300
 Jelimo sad vidjeti po čemu posljednja večera, dakle, ima prizvuk i jest mesijanska gozba,

1426
00:38:58,300 --> 00:39:02,080
 i svaka je uharistija, i, dakle, polovno skupljanje plemena.

1427
00:39:02,080 --> 00:39:02,780
 Na koji način?

1428
00:39:02,780 --> 00:39:05,920
 Marko 14, 17 od 25.

1429
00:39:05,920 --> 00:39:12,340
 A uvečer dođe on s 12-toricom, naravno, ne s trojicom, s šestoricom, 12-toricom.

1430
00:39:12,340 --> 00:39:13,620
 Da bude sve po PS-u.

1431
00:39:13,620 --> 00:39:14,420
 Molim?

1432
00:39:14,420 --> 00:39:16,260
 Ima neko-neko kakvo pitanje.

1433
00:39:16,260 --> 00:39:16,960
 Da, recite.

1434
00:39:16,960 --> 00:39:19,160
 Šta je?

1435
00:39:21,540 --> 00:39:22,180
 Petorku.

1436
00:39:22,180 --> 00:39:24,700
 Dobro.

1437
00:39:24,700 --> 00:39:25,880
 Ok.

1438
00:39:25,880 --> 00:39:30,440
 Dakle, i dok pijahu za stolom, te blagovahu, reče Isus.

1439
00:39:30,440 --> 00:39:33,660
 Zaista kažem vam, jedan će me od vas izdati.

1440
00:39:33,660 --> 00:39:35,300
 Koji stavlom blaguje?

1441
00:39:38,340 --> 00:39:38,860
 Dobro.

1442
00:39:38,860 --> 00:39:41,620
 O žalost će ni stavlom govoriti ja za drugim.

1443
00:39:41,620 --> 00:39:42,480
 Da nisam ja.

1444
00:39:42,480 --> 00:39:47,000
 A od im reče, jedan od dvane storice koji umače sa mnom u zdjelicu.

1445
00:39:47,000 --> 00:39:52,700
 Sin čovječi istina odlazi kako je o njemu pisano, ali ja o čovjeku onomu koji ga predaje.

1446
00:39:52,700 --> 00:39:55,500
 Tomu bi čovjeku bolje bilo da se ni rodio nije.

1447
00:39:56,260 --> 00:39:59,640
 I dok su blagovali, on uze kruh iz reče blagoslov pa razlobi.

1448
00:39:59,640 --> 00:40:01,260
 Razlobi, dade im i reče.

1449
00:40:01,260 --> 00:40:03,280
 Uzmite, ovo je tijelo moje.

1450
00:40:03,280 --> 00:40:05,420
 I uze čašu, zahvali i dade im.

1451
00:40:05,420 --> 00:40:06,600
 I svi su izljepili.

1452
00:40:06,600 --> 00:40:07,960
 A od im reče.

1453
00:40:07,960 --> 00:40:12,740
 Ovo je krv moja, krv saveza, koja se za mnoge proljeva.

1454
00:40:12,740 --> 00:40:14,360
 Ovdje ćemo objasniti.

1455
00:40:14,360 --> 00:40:17,660
 Dakle, ne za sve, nego za mnoge.

1456
00:40:18,540 --> 00:40:21,140
 Vjerojatno, možda neki do sad niste nije razumijeli razliku.

1457
00:40:21,140 --> 00:40:23,040
 Čuli je zapravo razliku.

1458
00:40:23,040 --> 00:40:27,120
 Zaista kažem vam, ne, neću više piti od ovoga roda trsova

1459
00:40:27,120 --> 00:40:31,860
 do onoga dana kad ću ga novoga piti u kraljevstvu Božem.

1460
00:40:31,860 --> 00:40:37,060
 Gotovo kao što je opisano u egzodusu Rabah ili u prorok Izalje.

1461
00:40:37,060 --> 00:40:41,620
 Ok, i dalje, Luka 22, 28-30 isto.

1462
00:40:41,620 --> 00:40:43,860
 Da, vi ste sa mnom ustrali u mojim kušnjama.

1463
00:40:43,860 --> 00:40:47,840
 Ja vam s toga u bašenu predajam kraljevstvu što ga je meni predao moj otac.

1464
00:40:47,840 --> 00:40:52,100
 Da jedete i pijete za mojim stolom u kraljevstvu Mojemu

1465
00:40:52,100 --> 00:40:56,300
 i sjedite na prijestoljima sudeći 12 plemena Izrelovih.

1466
00:40:56,300 --> 00:40:57,700
 Dakle, evo.

1467
00:40:57,700 --> 00:41:01,500
 Dakle, vi ste ti po kojima se po ovoj gozbi ovdje sada,

1468
00:41:01,500 --> 00:41:05,480
 tu ste 12 torica i vi ćete suditi 12 plemena Izrelovih.

1469
00:41:05,480 --> 00:41:08,260
 Vi ste novi vođe 12 plemena Izrelovih.

1470
00:41:08,260 --> 00:41:09,060
 Tako ih skuplja.

1471
00:41:09,060 --> 00:41:11,940
 Dobro, e sada, prije nego što krenemo,

1472
00:41:11,940 --> 00:41:15,560
 na kraju govorite o Isusovom času,

1473
00:41:15,560 --> 00:41:17,920
 kada će sve ljude privući k sebi,

1474
00:41:17,920 --> 00:41:19,820
 dakle, ne samo raspršene Izraelce,

1475
00:41:19,820 --> 00:41:23,300
 nego sve ljude, isto preko križe Euharistije,

1476
00:41:23,300 --> 00:41:27,740
 idemo samo ovdje riješiti problematiku

1477
00:41:27,740 --> 00:41:30,700
 da se njegova krv proljeva za mnoge,

1478
00:41:30,700 --> 00:41:31,620
 a ne za sve.

1479
00:41:31,620 --> 00:41:35,780
 Ja znate da na svetoj misi, u Hrvatskom,

1480
00:41:35,780 --> 00:41:37,560
 mi smo uvijek tolerantni,

1481
00:41:37,560 --> 00:41:38,440
 pa kažemo,

1482
00:41:38,440 --> 00:41:41,980
 ovo je, kak ide?

1483
00:41:41,980 --> 00:41:43,240
 Čekaj, ja čitam.

1484
00:41:44,540 --> 00:41:46,880
 Vi slušate, ste zapamtili kak to ide.

1485
00:41:46,880 --> 00:41:48,700
 Više sam 8 godina svećenik,

1486
00:41:48,700 --> 00:41:49,480
 ili...

1487
00:41:49,480 --> 00:41:49,960
 Tako je.

1488
00:41:49,960 --> 00:41:52,880
 Koja se proljeva za vas i za sve ljude.

1489
00:41:52,880 --> 00:41:53,580
 Ovo je važno.

1490
00:41:53,580 --> 00:41:56,840
 I odvaja za vas i za sve ljude.

1491
00:41:56,840 --> 00:41:59,220
 Ne kaže, koja se za sve vas proljeva,

1492
00:41:59,220 --> 00:42:01,240
 nego za vas i za sve ljude.

1493
00:42:01,240 --> 00:42:04,000
 Zapamtite ovu distinkciju koja se ovdje radi.

1494
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:05,380
 Tako i ovdje.

1495
00:42:08,040 --> 00:42:11,700
 Isto kaže, dakle, ovo je krv, moja krv saveza,

1496
00:42:11,700 --> 00:42:14,000
 koja se za mnoge proljeva.

1497
00:42:14,000 --> 00:42:18,420
 E sada, stvar je u tome,

1498
00:42:18,420 --> 00:42:20,900
 da kada radimo ovdje u svetoj misi,

1499
00:42:20,900 --> 00:42:24,060
 recimo i u latinskom isto,

1500
00:42:24,060 --> 00:42:25,920
 pro multis, ne pro omnibus,

1501
00:42:25,920 --> 00:42:27,940
 nego pro multis, za mnoge.

1502
00:42:27,940 --> 00:42:30,100
 Dakle, stvar je u tome,

1503
00:42:30,100 --> 00:42:32,460
 kada se ovdje radi razlika za vas,

1504
00:42:32,460 --> 00:42:35,840
 za židove i za sve ostale.

1505
00:42:35,840 --> 00:42:37,700
 Dakle, i za pogane.

1506
00:42:38,040 --> 00:42:40,040
 U hrvatskom, iako sam malo tražio,

1507
00:42:40,040 --> 00:42:41,460
 nema hrvatski samo to,

1508
00:42:41,460 --> 00:42:43,520
 ovo imaju drugi neki živi jezici

1509
00:42:43,520 --> 00:42:44,700
 koji isto tako naprave.

1510
00:42:44,700 --> 00:42:46,640
 Kada se ovdje kaže za mnoge,

1511
00:42:46,640 --> 00:42:50,940
 multitudo, dakle, ovdje je riječ

1512
00:42:50,940 --> 00:42:53,240
 o velikom mnoštvu.

1513
00:42:53,240 --> 00:42:56,460
 I to multitudo ima univerzalno značenje.

1514
00:42:56,460 --> 00:42:58,160
 Ne znači samo mnogo,

1515
00:42:58,160 --> 00:42:59,740
 nego može značiti i sve.

1516
00:42:59,740 --> 00:43:01,800
 Kada se kaže ovdje za mnoge,

1517
00:43:01,800 --> 00:43:03,580
 ovdje je spojeno sve,

1518
00:43:03,580 --> 00:43:06,300
 ovdje je spojeno vi i oni.

1519
00:43:06,620 --> 00:43:09,500
 Kada se kaže, govorim sada o jezišoj distinkciji,

1520
00:43:09,500 --> 00:43:10,780
 govorim sada o jeziku.

1521
00:43:10,780 --> 00:43:11,900
 Ovdje je jezik problem,

1522
00:43:11,900 --> 00:43:13,480
 gdje je problem spasenja.

1523
00:43:13,480 --> 00:43:15,440
 Naravno da je Isus umro za svakoga.

1524
00:43:15,440 --> 00:43:18,620
 Za svakoga i za svakoga je prolio svoju krv.

1525
00:43:18,620 --> 00:43:19,920
 Da se razumijemo.

1526
00:43:19,920 --> 00:43:21,580
 Ali ovdje je problem,

1527
00:43:21,580 --> 00:43:22,640
 zašto vam ovo govorim,

1528
00:43:22,640 --> 00:43:23,560
 ako vas neko pita,

1529
00:43:23,560 --> 00:43:24,500
 kao što sam ja imao,

1530
00:43:24,500 --> 00:43:26,020
 ja sam recimo imao problem s tim.

1531
00:43:26,460 --> 00:43:28,480
 Kad sam počeo kužiti tu razliku,

1532
00:43:28,480 --> 00:43:30,220
 kad sam počeo učiti jezike,

1533
00:43:30,220 --> 00:43:33,500
 anavajte, učiti jezike ponekad može biti komno za vašu vjeru.

1534
00:43:33,500 --> 00:43:37,080
 Kada sam kužio u latinskom promultis,

1535
00:43:37,080 --> 00:43:38,540
 vidim u grčkom isto tako,

1536
00:43:38,540 --> 00:43:40,140
 u izvodniku isto tako za mnoge,

1537
00:43:40,140 --> 00:43:41,840
 a ovdje za vas i za sve.

1538
00:43:41,840 --> 00:43:44,340
 Dakle, riječ je da za mnoge,

1539
00:43:44,340 --> 00:43:45,540
 podrazumljiva za vas,

1540
00:43:45,540 --> 00:43:46,120
 židove,

1541
00:43:46,120 --> 00:43:47,200
 on pred sovima židove,

1542
00:43:47,200 --> 00:43:48,200
 ima dvanestoricu.

1543
00:43:48,200 --> 00:43:50,000
 Dakle, i za sve.

1544
00:43:50,340 --> 00:43:52,540
 Ovo sve, misli se, za ostale,

1545
00:43:52,540 --> 00:43:54,620
 za pogane,

1546
00:43:54,620 --> 00:43:55,960
 za oni koji nisu židovi,

1547
00:43:55,960 --> 00:43:56,600
 za ne židove,

1548
00:43:56,600 --> 00:43:58,100
 za grke, rimljane itd.

1549
00:43:58,100 --> 00:44:01,460
 Zaključit ćemo sa onaj Isusov čas,

1550
00:44:01,460 --> 00:44:03,740
 kada će sve ljude privući k sebi.

1551
00:44:03,740 --> 00:44:06,220
 Dakle, ono, konačno sabiranje svih plemena.

1552
00:44:06,220 --> 00:44:11,400
 Iva dvanest, dvadeset do tristri kaže ovo.

1553
00:44:11,400 --> 00:44:16,640
 A među onima koji su došli klanjati na blagdan,

1554
00:44:16,640 --> 00:44:17,800
 bijahu i neki grci.

1555
00:44:18,840 --> 00:44:20,120
 Oni pristupe Filipu,

1556
00:44:20,120 --> 00:44:21,160
 grčko ime,

1557
00:44:21,160 --> 00:44:22,460
 naravno da će Filipu,

1558
00:44:22,460 --> 00:44:24,740
 zoveš se Filip pa se daš,

1559
00:44:24,740 --> 00:44:25,020
 jel da?

1560
00:44:25,020 --> 00:44:27,240
 Filipu iz Becajde, Galilejske,

1561
00:44:27,240 --> 00:44:27,860
 pa ga zamole.

1562
00:44:27,860 --> 00:44:29,800
 Gospodine, htjeli bismo vidjeti Isusa.

1563
00:44:29,800 --> 00:44:32,300
 Filip ode i kaže to Adri,

1564
00:44:32,300 --> 00:44:33,360
 drugo grčko ime,

1565
00:44:33,360 --> 00:44:33,820
 ili tako?

1566
00:44:33,820 --> 00:44:35,160
 Pogansko ime.

1567
00:44:35,160 --> 00:44:36,320
 Pa Adri i Filip,

1568
00:44:36,320 --> 00:44:38,080
 dva židova grčkih imena,

1569
00:44:38,080 --> 00:44:39,920
 odu i kažu Isusu.

1570
00:44:39,920 --> 00:44:41,060
 Isus im odgovori,

1571
00:44:41,060 --> 00:44:43,620
 došao je čas da se proslavi sin čovječi.

1572
00:44:43,620 --> 00:44:45,520
 Zašto je sad ovo taj čas?

1573
00:44:45,520 --> 00:44:47,280
 Zašto cijelo vrijeme odgađa čas i kaže,

1574
00:44:48,840 --> 00:44:51,200
 u istom evanđelju po Ivanu,

1575
00:44:51,200 --> 00:44:52,220
 druga glava,

1576
00:44:52,220 --> 00:44:53,680
 kada Marija kaže,

1577
00:44:53,680 --> 00:44:54,700
 vi da nemaju,

1578
00:44:54,700 --> 00:44:55,700
 a on kaže,

1579
00:44:55,700 --> 00:44:56,900
 ženo, što je vam s tobom,

1580
00:44:56,900 --> 00:44:58,120
 još nije došao moj čas.

1581
00:44:58,120 --> 00:44:59,780
 Još neki, još nije došao moj čas.

1582
00:44:59,780 --> 00:45:00,500
 Nego sada,

1583
00:45:00,500 --> 00:45:01,920
 zašto ovo je trenutak?

1584
00:45:01,920 --> 00:45:03,200
 Došao je čas.

1585
00:45:03,200 --> 00:45:04,300
 Jer ga traže grci,

1586
00:45:04,300 --> 00:45:05,340
 jer ga traže pogani.

1587
00:45:05,340 --> 00:45:07,600
 Došao je čas, jel?

1588
00:45:07,600 --> 00:45:10,920
 Dakle, čim su pogani počeli tražiti Isusa,

1589
00:45:10,920 --> 00:45:12,160
 Isus kaže,

1590
00:45:12,160 --> 00:45:13,160
 sada je došao,

1591
00:45:13,160 --> 00:45:14,140
 došao moj čas.

1592
00:45:14,140 --> 00:45:15,300
 To je to, ispunjenje, jel?

1593
00:45:15,300 --> 00:45:16,720
 Dakle, ne samo židovima,

1594
00:45:16,720 --> 00:45:17,780
 nego i poganima.

1595
00:45:17,780 --> 00:45:19,620
 Da se proslavi sin čovječi.

1596
00:45:19,620 --> 00:45:21,000
 I onda govor,

1597
00:45:21,000 --> 00:45:22,560
 zaista, zaista kaže vam,

1598
00:45:22,560 --> 00:45:23,560
 ako pšenično zrno,

1599
00:45:23,560 --> 00:45:24,460
 pavši na zemlju,

1600
00:45:24,460 --> 00:45:24,840
 ne umre,

1601
00:45:24,840 --> 00:45:25,580
 ostaje samo,

1602
00:45:25,580 --> 00:45:26,440
 a ko ne umre,

1603
00:45:26,440 --> 00:45:27,820
 donosi objelat rod.

1604
00:45:27,820 --> 00:45:28,640
 Dakle, vidite,

1605
00:45:28,640 --> 00:45:30,780
 poveznica između smrti i hrane,

1606
00:45:30,780 --> 00:45:31,960
 pšenično zrno, jel?

1607
00:45:31,960 --> 00:45:33,120
 Između, dakle,

1608
00:45:33,120 --> 00:45:35,200
 prehramdenog neke namjednice

1609
00:45:35,200 --> 00:45:36,200
 i smrti.

1610
00:45:36,200 --> 00:45:38,640
 Dakle, opet imamo gozba,

1611
00:45:38,640 --> 00:45:40,480
 koja će zapravo biti smrtolosna,

1612
00:45:40,480 --> 00:45:43,260
 kako će izgledati taj čas.

1613
00:45:43,260 --> 00:45:44,120
 I ono,

1614
00:45:44,120 --> 00:45:44,940
 tko ljubi svoj život,

1615
00:45:44,940 --> 00:45:45,540
 izgubi će ga,

1616
00:45:45,540 --> 00:45:47,020
 tko brzi svoj život na ovom svijetu,

1617
00:45:47,020 --> 00:45:49,080
 sačuvat će ga za život vječni.

1618
00:45:49,080 --> 00:45:49,880
 E, sada,

1619
00:45:49,880 --> 00:45:53,600
 u to dođe glas s neba.

1620
00:45:53,600 --> 00:45:54,840
 Ko je taj glas s neba?

1621
00:45:54,840 --> 00:45:55,660
 Očev glas.

1622
00:45:55,660 --> 00:45:56,720
 Samo tri puta,

1623
00:45:56,720 --> 00:45:58,580
 ovo je treći i posljednji puta,

1624
00:45:58,580 --> 00:45:59,440
 kada u Evanđelju

1625
00:45:59,440 --> 00:46:00,500
 imamo očev glas,

1626
00:46:00,500 --> 00:46:01,200
 glas s neba.

1627
00:46:01,200 --> 00:46:03,140
 Ovo je treći i posljednji puta,

1628
00:46:03,140 --> 00:46:05,940
 kada čujemo da otac nebeski govori.

1629
00:46:05,940 --> 00:46:07,480
 U to dođe glas s neba.

1630
00:46:07,880 --> 00:46:10,300
 Proslavio sam i opet ću proslaviti.

1631
00:46:10,300 --> 00:46:12,020
 Mnoštvo koje je od nje stajalo

1632
00:46:12,020 --> 00:46:12,600
 i slušalo,

1633
00:46:12,600 --> 00:46:13,900
 govoraše za grbjelo je.

1634
00:46:13,900 --> 00:46:15,220
 Drugi govorahu,

1635
00:46:15,220 --> 00:46:16,380
 anđel mu je zborio.

1636
00:46:16,380 --> 00:46:17,480
 Isus na to reče,

1637
00:46:17,480 --> 00:46:19,520
 ovaj glas nije bio poradi mene,

1638
00:46:19,520 --> 00:46:20,600
 nego poradi vas.

1639
00:46:20,600 --> 00:46:23,320
 Sada je sud ovome svijetu,

1640
00:46:23,320 --> 00:46:27,100
 sada će knez ovoga svijeta biti izbačen.

1641
00:46:27,100 --> 00:46:29,660
 Dakle, križ kao univerzalni egzorcizam.

1642
00:46:29,660 --> 00:46:33,660
 Dakle, možemo imati ciklus kateheza

1643
00:46:33,660 --> 00:46:37,860
 na temu križ kao univerzalni egzorcizam.

1644
00:46:37,880 --> 00:46:43,020
 Ono što isto imamo, dakle,

1645
00:46:43,020 --> 00:46:45,240
 kod proroka Ezekijela,

1646
00:46:45,240 --> 00:46:49,420
 kod proroka Ezekijela se stavlja znak križa na čelu,

1647
00:46:49,420 --> 00:46:52,040
 da se zna, dakle, isto neki ukrštani znak.

1648
00:46:52,040 --> 00:46:54,980
 Dakle, imate te povezanost križa i egzorcizma

1649
00:46:54,980 --> 00:46:57,540
 isto kod proroka, isto u starom zajetu i tako dalje.

1650
00:46:57,700 --> 00:46:59,440
 To isto može biti jedno zadimljivo.

1651
00:46:59,440 --> 00:47:01,580
 Evo, ok, možda, jednog dana.

1652
00:47:01,580 --> 00:47:04,600
 Dakle, sada će knez ovoga svijeta biti izbačen.

1653
00:47:04,600 --> 00:47:06,220
 Križ kao univerzalni egzorcizam.

1654
00:47:06,220 --> 00:47:09,200
 A ja kada budem uznignut sa zemlje,

1655
00:47:09,200 --> 00:47:10,800
 sve ću privući k sebi.

1656
00:47:10,800 --> 00:47:13,140
 Sve ću privući k sebi.

1657
00:47:13,140 --> 00:47:13,800
 Dakle, sve.

1658
00:47:13,800 --> 00:47:16,500
 Ne mnoge, nego sve ću privući k sebi.

1659
00:47:16,500 --> 00:47:20,680
 I sada, ovdje mi je onako se lijepo zaključuje, zaokružuje.

1660
00:47:20,680 --> 00:47:24,620
 Dakle, imate ovaj, kak se zove,

1661
00:47:24,620 --> 00:47:27,300
 pardon, pardon, pardon, pardon.

1662
00:47:27,300 --> 00:47:30,180
 Kaže, kada će to biti,

1663
00:47:30,180 --> 00:47:34,220
 kada budem uznignut sa zemlje,

1664
00:47:34,220 --> 00:47:35,120
 sve ću privući k sebi.

1665
00:47:35,120 --> 00:47:37,220
 Znači, on će privući svek sebi kada bude što?

1666
00:47:37,220 --> 00:47:38,160
 Uzdignut.

1667
00:47:38,160 --> 00:47:40,340
 Kada je sve Isus uznignut?

1668
00:47:40,340 --> 00:47:42,020
 Kada je sve Isus uznignut?

1669
00:47:42,020 --> 00:47:45,920
 Križ, uznignut je u trenutku skrsnuća,

1670
00:47:46,500 --> 00:47:49,380
 uznignut je u trenutku uzašašća.

1671
00:47:49,380 --> 00:47:51,140
 Dakle, kada, jer uznašašćem,

1672
00:47:51,140 --> 00:47:53,400
 on kreće pripremati nebesku gozbu

1673
00:47:53,400 --> 00:47:55,640
 i kada će on uznašašćem u nebu biti

1674
00:47:55,640 --> 00:47:57,040
 naša stalna žrtva.

1675
00:47:57,040 --> 00:47:59,360
 Stalno prinošenje samoga sveme gospodinu.

1676
00:47:59,360 --> 00:48:00,840
 Zato je uznašašće važno.

1677
00:48:00,840 --> 00:48:04,780
 I kada je još Isus uznignut sa zemlje?

1678
00:48:04,780 --> 00:48:07,420
 Na svakoj svetoj misi.

1679
00:48:07,420 --> 00:48:09,600
 Dakle, to je taj znak, to je ta gesta.

1680
00:48:09,600 --> 00:48:11,360
 U najključnjem dijelu sve te mise,

1681
00:48:11,360 --> 00:48:12,420
 pod pretvorom,

1682
00:48:12,420 --> 00:48:14,220
 Krist je uznignut.

1683
00:48:14,680 --> 00:48:16,480
 Dakle, sa zemlje.

1684
00:48:16,480 --> 00:48:18,440
 I tada će sve privući k sebi.

1685
00:48:18,440 --> 00:48:20,940
 Kolike sve te mise od posljednje večere

1686
00:48:20,940 --> 00:48:23,260
 koje su privukle i obratile

1687
00:48:23,260 --> 00:48:24,500
 na milijarde.

1688
00:48:24,500 --> 00:48:27,500
 Ako uzmete stoljeća,

1689
00:48:27,500 --> 00:48:28,640
 tisuć ljeća

1690
00:48:28,640 --> 00:48:30,140
 koja su od posljednje večere

1691
00:48:30,140 --> 00:48:31,660
 i od ovoga što se dogodilo

1692
00:48:31,660 --> 00:48:34,340
 u vazbenom trodnevnju.

1693
00:48:34,340 --> 00:48:36,240
 I zato, dakle, ovo,

1694
00:48:36,240 --> 00:48:38,180
 a ja kad budem uznignut sa zemlje,

1695
00:48:38,180 --> 00:48:39,960
 sve ću privući k sebi.

1696
00:48:39,960 --> 00:48:42,760
 Dakle, Evanđelje nije poezija.

1697
00:48:43,900 --> 00:48:45,680
 Isus ne koristi neke motive

1698
00:48:45,680 --> 00:48:47,100
 poetično.

1699
00:48:47,100 --> 00:48:48,580
 Uznignut sa zemlje,

1700
00:48:48,580 --> 00:48:50,120
 sve ću preneseno.

1701
00:48:50,120 --> 00:48:52,180
 Jer on govori,

1702
00:48:52,180 --> 00:48:54,000
 što ono kad kaže,

1703
00:48:54,000 --> 00:48:56,360
 ako ne jedete tijela sina čovječega,

1704
00:48:56,360 --> 00:48:57,480
 ne pijete njegove krvi,

1705
00:48:57,480 --> 00:48:59,320
 nemate života u sebi.

1706
00:48:59,320 --> 00:49:00,860
 I onda kad svi odlaze,

1707
00:49:00,860 --> 00:49:01,340
 što kaže?

1708
00:49:01,340 --> 00:49:02,080
 Bada je šalio sam se,

1709
00:49:02,080 --> 00:49:02,800
 to je metaforika,

1710
00:49:02,800 --> 00:49:04,020
 to je simbolično značenje.

1711
00:49:04,020 --> 00:49:05,620
 Ne, to je konkretno značenje,

1712
00:49:05,620 --> 00:49:06,600
 to fakat tako stoji.

1713
00:49:07,040 --> 00:49:09,640
 Dakle, ovdje će stvarno biti uznignut sa zemlje

1714
00:49:09,640 --> 00:49:11,860
 i stvarno će tada sve privući k sebi.

1715
00:49:11,860 --> 00:49:15,220
 I to je ono što sam na početku stavio

1716
00:49:15,220 --> 00:49:17,060
 kod Izaije 11.10.20,

1717
00:49:17,060 --> 00:49:18,200
 time smo i započeli.

1718
00:49:19,320 --> 00:49:21,440
 U ovaj dan njišev izdanak Mesija

1719
00:49:21,440 --> 00:49:23,920
 dignut kao stijeg narodima.

1720
00:49:23,920 --> 00:49:25,680
 Uzdignut sa zemlje.

1721
00:49:25,680 --> 00:49:28,400
 Dakle, podignut će stijeg narodima

1722
00:49:28,400 --> 00:49:31,180
 i on će biti dignut kao stijeg narodima.

1723
00:49:31,180 --> 00:49:34,940
 Puci će ga željno tražiti.

1724
00:49:34,940 --> 00:49:36,900
 Evo, svi bi ovdje zaključio.

1725
00:49:36,900 --> 00:49:39,080
 Dobro, je li ovo sve jasno?

1726
00:49:39,080 --> 00:49:41,880
 Ok, razumijeli ste, dobro.

1727
00:49:41,880 --> 00:49:43,120
 Još ne razumijete.

1728
00:49:43,120 --> 00:49:45,080
 Ok, dobro.

1729
00:49:45,080 --> 00:49:46,800
 Sljedeći puta, e sada,

1730
00:49:46,800 --> 00:49:48,040
 dakle, ono što sam rekao,

1731
00:49:48,420 --> 00:49:50,280
 ovo sve, ako je sjelo,

1732
00:49:50,280 --> 00:49:52,140
 onda smo prešli onu granicu,

1733
00:49:52,140 --> 00:49:56,240
 dobro, Euharistija kao dio ispunjenja,

1734
00:49:56,240 --> 00:49:58,860
 ne dio, ispunjenje, konkretno ispunjenje,

1735
00:49:58,860 --> 00:50:01,300
 ovo je sve svih židovskih nada,

1736
00:50:01,300 --> 00:50:02,920
 nada na iščekivanje i tako dalje.

1737
00:50:02,920 --> 00:50:04,860
 Evo, kroz proroke,

1738
00:50:04,860 --> 00:50:07,980
 kroz, dakle, samu židovsku tradiciju

1739
00:50:07,980 --> 00:50:11,380
 i naravno ono što je za našu odjelenu braću

1740
00:50:11,380 --> 00:50:13,600
 isto važno, kroz same Isusove riječi.

1741
00:50:13,600 --> 00:50:17,140
 Međutim, gdje je tu onda ona konkretna prisutnost?

1742
00:50:17,520 --> 00:50:19,100
 Znaš to, kažem,

1743
00:50:19,100 --> 00:50:21,120
 kod Euharistije idemo još korak dalje

1744
00:50:21,120 --> 00:50:23,440
 i kažemo da ta mesijanska gozba

1745
00:50:23,440 --> 00:50:25,500
 nije samo gozba, dakle,

1746
00:50:25,500 --> 00:50:27,500
 od žrtvovanoga, od pretiline i vina,

1747
00:50:27,500 --> 00:50:29,140
 fina, staložene i tako dalje,

1748
00:50:29,140 --> 00:50:32,160
 nego da pod tim žrtvovanom je njegovo tijelo,

1749
00:50:32,160 --> 00:50:34,820
 dakle, pretilo,

1750
00:50:34,820 --> 00:50:36,560
 nije su, tijelo bilo pretilo,

1751
00:50:36,560 --> 00:50:37,520
 pa je zato pretilina,

1752
00:50:37,520 --> 00:50:39,200
 ovaj, dakle, meso,

1753
00:50:39,200 --> 00:50:41,360
 nego i pod prilikama vina,

1754
00:50:41,360 --> 00:50:42,060
 njegova krv.

1755
00:50:42,120 --> 00:50:44,340
 zašto idemo u konkretnu prisutnost,

1756
00:50:44,340 --> 00:50:45,460
 a ne samo neka gozba,

1757
00:50:45,460 --> 00:50:46,720
 spome gozba i tako dalje.

1758
00:50:46,720 --> 00:50:48,140
 Evo, sljedeći puta,

1759
00:50:48,140 --> 00:50:49,860
 nazvao sam,

1760
00:50:49,860 --> 00:50:52,340
 predavanje za sljedeći puta,

1761
00:50:52,340 --> 00:50:53,620
 četvrta čaša

1762
00:50:53,620 --> 00:50:55,140
 i nova paska,

1763
00:50:55,140 --> 00:50:55,700
 odnosno izlazak.

1764
00:50:55,760 --> 00:50:57,800
 Što je ta četvrta čaša?

1765
00:50:57,800 --> 00:50:59,220
 Vi se sjećate da Isus kaže

1766
00:50:59,220 --> 00:51:00,760
 u Gecemaniji,

1767
00:51:00,760 --> 00:51:03,740
 oče, rekao sam,

1768
00:51:03,740 --> 00:51:05,840
 ono što Isus govori nije poetično,

1769
00:51:05,840 --> 00:51:07,780
 nego ima konkretno značenje.

1770
00:51:07,780 --> 00:51:08,720
 Kada Isus kaže,

1771
00:51:08,720 --> 00:51:09,920
 oče, ako je moguće,

1772
00:51:09,920 --> 00:51:11,880
 neka me mi bojđe ova čaša

1773
00:51:11,880 --> 00:51:12,520
 ili ovaj kalež,

1774
00:51:12,520 --> 00:51:13,960
 ovisi, dakle, o prijevodu.

1775
00:51:13,960 --> 00:51:15,600
 Od toga kaže preneseno,

1776
00:51:15,600 --> 00:51:16,920
 nego koja je to čaša,

1777
00:51:16,920 --> 00:51:17,760
 koja je to kalež.

1778
00:51:17,760 --> 00:51:19,640
 Zašto, dakle,

1779
00:51:19,640 --> 00:51:21,680
 kada ste imali slavlje pashe,

1780
00:51:21,680 --> 00:51:24,560
 dakle, govorimo o živijevskom slavlju pashe,

1781
00:51:24,560 --> 00:51:27,200
 prisutne su četiri čaše,

1782
00:51:27,200 --> 00:51:28,480
 pashalne, četiri,

1783
00:51:28,480 --> 00:51:29,880
 četiri kaleža pashalna.

1784
00:51:29,880 --> 00:51:32,320
 I to je ključ,

1785
00:51:32,320 --> 00:51:33,320
 da vidimo sad,

1786
00:51:33,320 --> 00:51:34,240
 idemo korak dalje,

1787
00:51:34,240 --> 00:51:36,860
 vidjeti kako iz živijevske perspektive

1788
00:51:36,860 --> 00:51:37,840
 isto shvatiti,

1789
00:51:37,840 --> 00:51:39,040
 da možda zaista riječi

1790
00:51:39,040 --> 00:51:41,380
 o nekoj konkretnoj prisutnosti božarskoj

1791
00:51:41,380 --> 00:51:42,560
 pod prilikama kruha i vijena.

1792
00:51:42,560 --> 00:51:43,880
 Tako da sljedeći puta,

1793
00:51:43,880 --> 00:51:45,680
 kako je zlala pashu Isus ovo vrijeme,

1794
00:51:45,680 --> 00:51:46,500
 to nam je važno,

1795
00:51:46,500 --> 00:51:48,560
 što su Petar i Ivan

1796
00:51:48,560 --> 00:51:49,800
 zapravo činili

1797
00:51:49,800 --> 00:51:51,340
 kada su otešli u Jeruzalem

1798
00:51:51,340 --> 00:51:52,280
 pripraviti pashu,

1799
00:51:52,280 --> 00:51:53,900
 dakle, to je detalj

1800
00:51:53,900 --> 00:51:54,940
 koji tako pročitamo

1801
00:51:54,940 --> 00:51:55,440
 i prođemo.

1802
00:51:55,440 --> 00:51:56,680
 Međutim, vrlo značajno,

1803
00:51:56,680 --> 00:51:57,380
 vrlo važno.

1804
00:51:57,380 --> 00:51:59,640
 Zašto su četiri čaše vina

1805
00:51:59,640 --> 00:52:01,500
 potrebne za svako slavlje pashe?

1806
00:52:01,500 --> 00:52:04,000
 Koji su dijelovi razine,

1807
00:52:04,000 --> 00:52:04,560
 ajmo reći,

1808
00:52:04,560 --> 00:52:06,000
 koji je red slavljena pashe?

1809
00:52:06,000 --> 00:52:07,280
 Ordo pashe,

1810
00:52:07,280 --> 00:52:08,020
 ajmo reći,

1811
00:52:08,020 --> 00:52:09,700
 i kako odgovaraju dijelovima

1812
00:52:09,700 --> 00:52:10,880
 redu svete mise?

1813
00:52:10,880 --> 00:52:13,260
 I je li Isus zapravo

1814
00:52:13,260 --> 00:52:14,940
 zaključio posljednju večeru?

1815
00:52:15,580 --> 00:52:20,320
 To je ono što nas čeka sljedeći puta.

1816
00:52:20,320 --> 00:52:20,680
 Ok?

1817
00:52:20,680 --> 00:52:21,820
 Sljedeći utorak,

1818
00:52:21,820 --> 00:52:22,820
 vidimo se ovdje.

1819
00:52:22,820 --> 00:52:23,640
 Evo.

1820
00:52:32,120 --> 00:52:32,560
 Dobro.

1821
00:52:32,560 --> 00:52:34,180
 Idemo sada nešto jesti pit.

1822
00:52:34,180 --> 00:52:36,380
 Toko o gozbi i tako dalje,

1823
00:52:36,380 --> 00:52:37,280
 vjerojatno ste ogladnili.

1824
00:52:37,280 --> 00:52:38,060
 Ok.

1825
00:52:38,060 --> 00:52:40,320
 U ima Oca i Sina i Duha Svetoga.

1826
00:52:40,320 --> 00:52:40,700
 Amen.

1827
00:52:40,700 --> 00:52:43,460
 Slava Ocu i Sinu i Duhu Svetomu,

1828
00:52:43,460 --> 00:52:45,480
 kako bi jaš na početku,

1829
00:52:45,480 --> 00:52:47,380
 tako i sada i vazda,

1830
00:52:47,380 --> 00:52:49,200
 i u vijeke, vijekova.

1831
00:52:49,200 --> 00:52:49,720
 Amen.

1832
00:52:49,720 --> 00:52:51,620
 U ima Oca i Sina i Duha Svetoga.

1833
00:52:51,620 --> 00:52:51,780
 Amen.

